currentDoc: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

currentSuggestions.original: This new collective mind, called the Consciousness, is a remarkable phenomenon.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: This new collective mind, called the Consciousness, is a remarkable phenomenon.

currentSuggestions.original: This power gives them the ability to cure all disease, to control matter, and to end hunger.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: This power gives them the ability to cure all disease, to control matter, and to end hunger.

currentSuggestions.original: They begin to form the human hive mind, their thoughts and actions in concert.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: They begin to form the human hive mind, their thoughts and actions in concert.

currentSuggestions.original: This power grants them the ability to work together to accomplish tasks that no one individual could do on their own.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: This power grants them the ability to work together to accomplish tasks that no one individual could do on their own.

currentSuggestions.original: But it comes with a terrible price.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: But it comes with a terrible price.

ops.insert: This new collective mind, called the Consciousness, is a remarkable phenomenon.

currentSuggestions.original: When a person is linked to the Consciousness, they can learn and gain knowledge rapidly.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: When a person is linked to the Consciousness, they can learn and gain knowledge rapidly.

currentSuggestions.original: But it is also a weapon that can give humanity the edge it needs to drive back the Ethereal invaders.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: But it is also a weapon that can give humanity the edge it needs to drive back the Ethereal invaders.
